{"tid":32721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傅振中帶隊「支持CY捍衛領土」 晚上到泛民集會踩場","createTime":"2016-12-10T10:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T15:06:39.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c7941105a5d8ebd44a30b907e68c5964e4f40c55","tid":32721,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161210/large/1481365656_10d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F1481365656_10d2.jpg&h=385e3116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n26位「民主派會議」議員早前召開記者會，呼籲市民今晚參與「689搞政變，向市民宣戰」集會，向特首梁振英還擊，集會將於晚上7時半中環遮打花園舉行；「保衛香港運動」傍晚在國金交易廣場外舉行集會，聲稱要「支持CY捍衛領土」，並打算遊行至遮打花園外踩場，現場約20人出席。<br />\n<br />\n主席傅振中指要泛民才是撕裂社會的始作俑者，認為泛民議員要入獄走數，不應賴特首梁振英撕裂社會。<br />\n<br />\n民主派早前已取得不反對通知書，申請集會人數為3,000人。民主派會議召集人涂謹申希望，行動能凝聚最多市民，支持民主派議員，尤其被政府入稟取消資格的議員。涂謹申指，政府今次司法覆核舉動，是衝著9月立法會選舉結果而來，是希望推翻當時大選結果，否定市民當時選擇。"},{"pid":"da92c0b282b50d0e9f66d91c029ade87e7690f41","tid":32721,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:57:28.000Z","msg":"仲向689還擊？"},{"pid":"5d4aed4e6644f3855bd529c7546cd82ca5c12c4e","tid":32721,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:18:01.000Z","msg":"回帶？"},{"pid":"085dee1c493c950f3642d771908486b6ab432f4d","tid":32721,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:23:03.000Z","msg":"cy 有領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6c96e3aed0768c571b7a32b3256997188fa8ae","tid":32721,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:39:43.000Z","msg":"送上門俾人恥笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3af851f4d3ae16cf7143edf27b596e74cf68014","tid":32721,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T12:04:14.000Z","msg":"港獨之父嘅領土 <img src=\"/ass